Token.Abstract: An MD5 digest of the non-URL-encoded message attribute string. This can be used to verify that Amazon SQS received the message correctly. Amazon SQS first URL decodes the message before creating the MD5 digest. For information about MD5, go to http://www.faqs.org/rfcs/rfc1321.html.
